        "content": "<p>Hi all! Yesterday, I sent a <a href=\"https://lore.kernel.org/rust-for-linux/tencent_6FBA3773CF74B276166B63D292CB2E8D3D07@qq.com/\">patch</a>  about the UIO device abstraction, to support writing UIO driver in Rust. <br>\nI try reimplement <code>bio_cif.c</code> in rust, and got a problem: How to obtain <code>SampleDriver.bar0</code> in <code>SampleUioDevice </code>? <br>\nMaybe my abstraction is a bad design? <span aria-label=\"thinking\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f914\" role=\"img\" title=\"thinking\">:thinking:</span></p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">SampleDriver</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">pdev</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">pci</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Device</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">_registration</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Pin</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">KBox</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">uio</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Registration</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">SampleUioDevice</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">_bar0</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Devres</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Bar</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">pci_device_table</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"p\">.);</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">pci</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Driver</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">SampleDriver</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">IdInfo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">();</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">const</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ID_TABLE</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">pci</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">IdTable</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">IdInfo</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">PCI_TABLE</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">probe</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">pdev</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">pci</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Device</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_info</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">IdInfo</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Pin</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">KBox</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">dev_dbg</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">pdev</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">as_ref</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"s\">\"Probe Rust PCI driver sample (PCI ID: 0x{:x}, 0x{:x}).</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s\">\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">pdev</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">vendor_id</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">pdev</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">device_id</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">pdev</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">enable_device_mem</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"o\">?</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bar0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">pdev</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">iomap_region_sized</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c_str</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"rust_driver_pci0\"</span><span class=\"p\">))</span><span class=\"o\">?</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">options</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">UioDeviceOptions</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">new</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c_str</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"0.0.1\"</span><span class=\"p\">));</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">registration</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">KBox</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">uio</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Registration</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">register</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">THIS_MODULE</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">pdev</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">as_ref</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">options</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">GFP_KERNEL</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">?</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">drvdata</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">KBox</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">new</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"n\">pdev</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">pdev</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">clone</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"n\">_registration</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">registration</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"n\">_bar0</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">bar0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">},</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">GFP_KERNEL</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">?</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">drvdata</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">into</span><span class=\"p\">())</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">SampleUioDevice</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"cp\">#[vtable]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">uio</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">UioDevice</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">SampleUioDevice</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Ptr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Pin</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">KBox</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">open</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">info</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">Info</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Ptr</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">KBox</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">new</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">},</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">GFP_KERNEL</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">?</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">into</span><span class=\"p\">())</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">handler</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">device</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Pin</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">SampleUioDevice</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_info</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">Info</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_irq</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">ffi</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">c_int</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">IrqReturn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"c1\">// need to access `bar0` in the `SampleDriver `</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 488653308,
